d_subtitle.message: Isin haadhu hundaaf achi kennanii, gama duraatii, gama dhibbaatii fi qoonqooti ummataa hunda irraa hordofe. Dhaabbannoonni dhiyaa irratti akka hin qabne, haadha isin hordofu!
